title: The REAL Reason We Signed Up for 'The Bachelor'
description:
Sadie is joined by "Bachelor" alums Sean and Catherine Lowe to talk about how they first caught each other's attention, the real reason they signed up to be reality TV stars, how they create a fun-filled home for their kids, and why God, humor, laughter, and fun are so important in their lives.
